data.description: Stunning city retreat! Tranquility awaits in this fully renovated townhouse in the coveted Monterra neighborhood! Enjoy 9’ft ceilings, open concept floor plan, new quartz chef's kitchen + SS appliances, spacious living/dining complete with custom buffet and fireplace. Spacious bedrooms with custom closet organizers & full size laundry. No detail was overlooked! New flooring throughout, paint, carpet, bathrooms and more. Enjoy a 2-car tandem garage. Relax in the fenced backyard with mature garden and lots of light! Set in serene neighborhood with 7 rain-gardens and two waterfalls! Conveniently located to the new LIGHT RAIL, shopping, restaurants, trails and I-5 N/S. So much to see, don't wait! Special Financing Rates!
